    {
      "id": "PopularPost325855",
      "post_content": "> sac three [blood pet](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=blood pet)s  \n> [buried alive](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=buried alive) -> three [nether shadow](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=nether shadow)s  \n> [fossil find](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=fossil find) the pets over the spirits so they can trigger next upkeep  \n> you have now searched your library for three 1/1s with haste for the low low cost of.... er.... {2}{B}![Red or Green](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=RG&type=symbol). which is cheaper than {B}{B}{B}{B}{B}{B}, but not really by much. and you could always just lose the spirits to fossil find, which is kinda lame.  \n  \nnot to mention you'd need to draw three blood pets and buried alive. but hey, maybe you're running demonic tutor or something. i would use that for something better but, heh.",
      "posted_by": "NARFNra",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost325855\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">&gt; sac three <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"blood pet\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=blood pet\">blood pet</a>s<br/>&gt; <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"buried alive\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=buried alive\">buried alive</a> -&gt; three <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"nether shadow\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=nether shadow\">nether shadow</a>s<br/>&gt; <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"fossil find\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=fossil find\">fossil find</a> the pets over the spirits so they can trigger next upkeep<br/>&gt; you have now searched your library for three 1/1s with haste for the low low cost of.... er.... {2}{B}<img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red or Green\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=RG&amp;type=symbol\"/>. which is cheaper than {B}{B}{B}{B}{B}{B}, but not really by much. and you could always just lose the spirits to fossil find, which is kinda lame.<br/><br/>not to mention you'd need to draw three blood pets and buried alive. but hey, maybe you're running demonic tutor or something. i would use that for something better but, heh.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '325855'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n             